Acknowledgement

Modern civilization has a long journey ahead to acknowledge and address the historic and ongoing impacts of colonialism that have resulted in harm to the cultures and livelihoods living interconnected with our ecosystems for many thousands of years.

Tributary to Parsnip River - 125000

A map of the watershed is provided in map attachment 93I.111.


In 2019 a video survey was conducted by drone and can be viewed here. In the summer of 2022 additional surveys were conducted with resulting images stitched into an orthomosaic and 3-dimensional model. Surveys were conducted with a remotely piloted aircraft at the crossing with resulting images stitched into an orthomosaic and 3-dimensional model presented here and here.
